---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">深水埗手機零件店<br /><span class="hero-highlight">iPhone・Samsung・華為 零件目錄</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        MonCity 換Mon城位於深水埗深之都，售賣 iPhone、Samsung、華為、小米、Pixel 等
        手機零件 — 前螢幕玻璃、螢幕總成、後蓋玻璃、電池、Face ID 模組、排線。
        原裝及副廠選擇，門市現貨。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/parts/" class="btn btn-primary"
          onclick="gtag('event','parts_click',{event_category:'navigation',event_label:'hero'})">
          📋 查看零件目錄
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/85269960711?text=%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%9B%B6%E4%BB%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%82%E5%9E%8B%E8%99%9F%EF%BC%9A" class="btn btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          onclick="gtag('event','whatsapp_click',{event_category:'contact',event_label:'hero'})">
          💬 WhatsApp 報型號查價
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span>✅ 門市現貨</span>
        <span>✅ 原裝 / 副廠</span>
        <span>✅ 批發零售</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, var(--paper) 100%);
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 800px; }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero-highlight { color: var(--primary); }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 48px 0 40px; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-actions .btn { text-align: center; justify-content: center; }
    .hero-trust { gap: 12px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }
</style>
